  "changelog": "# Sharkord Desktop v0.5.41 Beta\n\n## Fixes\n\n- Moves member role weighting out of personal Appearance settings and into server Role Management.\n- Adds server-side role weight persistence and migration; Owner starts at 0, other seeded roles at 100.\n- Sorts members by the highest-priority assigned role: lower weight numbers appear higher; larger numbers rank lower.\n- Fixes Retention Policy buttons using dark themed controls instead of white-on-white defaults.\n- Tightens Server Settings > Parity card layout to avoid clipped/dirty control arrangement.\n- Increases plugin marketplace card height so long descriptions are not clipped.\n- Stabilizes user status/date badge row to reduce flicker/layout shift.\n\nStable channel stays unchanged.\n",
